title: Ep. 307 - Trump Is More Principled Than His Critics
description:
As fake conservatives send leftists to mock pro-lifers at CPAC, environmentalist Congresswoman AOC guzzles fossil fuels, and Democrats double down on anti-Semitism and racial bigotry, one thing has become abundantly clear: President Trump is more principled than his critics. Then, what a documentary about Michael Jackson molesting little kids can tell us about our political culture. Date: 03-04-2019
